Manual iteration-15 strict hypoxia curation ledger created from NCBI GEO ESearch/ESummary queries for hypoxia/normoxia bulk RNA-seq candidates, GEO supplementary FTP listings, direct downloads of active candidate source files under data/deg/raw/iter15, temporary inspection of additional candidate workbooks in /tmp/degora_iter15_probe, pandas row/column audits, and sha256sum checks. Three independent strict S0 sources were activated; inspected candidates were excluded when they lacked contrast-level LFC plus p/FDR statistics, had <10000 reported rows, lacked >=3 matched biological replicates per arm, or confounded oxygen condition with another perturbation.
